      <h2>France's Maritime Neighbors</h2>
      <p>France shares a maritime border with <strong>37 States and territories</strong> — 30 sovereign States and 7 territories with their own Exclusive Economic Zone (EEZ). No other country in the world has as many maritime neighbors.</p>

